survey_response.review_text: We have been consulting Dr Radhalakshmi for the past 2 years. She is never in a hurry, takes ample time to check my child and explains everything in detail. My daughter cries a lot when placed in a hospital environment. But, the Doctor remains patient and tries to assuage her with lolly pops and lovely talks.  She is not only child friendly, but also parent friendly. She grasps what is going on within us and makes sure to clear all the doubts. More and more doctors like her are needed for our society.
